Package Service

package Service
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    ClearResult
    Class for the result body of the clear service
    ClearService
    Class that Deletes ALL data from the database, including user accounts, auth tokens, and generated person and event data.
    EventResult
    Class that contains the result of the Event service
    EventService
    Class that returns ALL events for ALL family members of the current user.
    FillRequest
    Class for the request info of the fill service
    FillResult
    Class for the result body of the fill service
    FillService
    Class that populates the server's database with generated data for the specified user name.
    LoadRequest
    Class for the request body of the load service
    LoadResult
    Class for the result body of the load service
    LoadService
    Class that clears all data from the database (just like the /clear API), and then loads the posted user, person, and event data into the database.
    LoginRequest
    Class for the request body of the login service
    LoginResult
    Class for the result body of the login service
    LoginService
    Class that logs in the user and returns an auth token.
    PersonResult
    Class for the result body of the person service
    PersonService
    Class that returns ALL family members of the current user.
    RegisterRequest
    Class for the request body of the register service
    RegisterResult
    Class for the result body of the register service
    RegisterService
    Class that creates a new user account, generates 4 generations of ancestor data for the new user, logs the user in, and returns an auth token.
    Result
    Abstract class of result, which holds values of a message and boolean for all other result classes to build off of
    SingleEventRequest
    Class for the request body of the /event/[eventID] service
    SingleEventResult
    Class for the result body of the /event/[eventID] service
    SingleEventService
    Class that returns the single Event object with the specified ID.
    SinglePersonRequest
    Class for the request body of the /person/[personID] service
    SinglePersonResult
    Class for the result body of the /person/[personID] service
    SinglePersonService
    Class that returns the single Service.Person object with the specified ID.
